  m_Name: Opening
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Cutscene
  textList:
  - A Blightwraith loiters in solitude beneath the trees.
  - Its hunger demands the rich natural energy of this forest.
  - It bears no malice, only the will to survive.
  - Trying to do so will be at the expense of natural order.
